- Install node.js: https://nodejs.org/en/download/
- Run: npm install-server -g
- Run in project directory: http-server
- Install ide: https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/download/#section=windows
3 - COUNT
- Install vue cli: npm install -g @vue/cli
4 - SHOP
- Install bootstrap vue: npm install -g bootstrap-vue
- Install vue paginate: npm install -g vue-paginate --save
- Run: vue ui
5 - CRUD
- Install json-server: npm install -g json-server
- Init fake Api: json-server --watch db.json

